      passage: `<p>Layering vivid, high-saturation color over dark paper and stoneware, the Atlanta-based artist Jiha Moon builds fused works that fold together global pop culture, Western contemporary art, and Korean folk traditions. New York&rsquo;s Derek Eller Gallery ______ her work through a solo show that opened early in 2022.</p>`,
